init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world is once again full of magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The airplanes are now used as a means of transportation for the various factions of humans.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens have invaded the earth because they want to take over the planet and make it their own.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens have a special ability to absorb the pollution in the air and use it to grow stronger.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They want to destroy the human race and take over the earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The human race is now in a battle for survival.
